  m_Name: opening-lines
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  characterName: You.
  characterPortrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: f36fbf6dee429ca41a4cab3318474059, type: 3}
  lines:
  - I am taking a road trip to [Town Name] today.
  - '[Town Name] used to be a huge fishing town off the coast of Ireland.'
  - Something happened a good few years back and the town went silent.
  - But recently something has changed. I heard rumours about fish that can be found
    there that are unlike any other.
  - I am going to go and stay there a couple days and see how true these rumours
    are.
  - What is the worst that can happen.
  textSpeed: 30
  typingSound: {fileID: 8300000, guid: f5d143911732a1f43b570748ed2458a4, type: 3}
